3
) sclerotised but without setae. Antemetaspiracular setae (am 
3
s) absent. Metathoracic spiracle (sp 
3
): width of peritreme 31–33 μm. Metasternum (stn 
3
) membranous throughout. Anterior metasternal setae (amss) and posterior metasternal setae (pmss) absent.
